18-0.query:
SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
FROM cat_cast_info_4 AS ci,
   cat_info_type_4 AS it1,
   cat_info_type_4 AS it2,
   cat_movie_info_4 AS mi,
   cat_movie_info_idx_4 AS mi_idx,
   cat_name_4 AS n,
   cat_title_4 AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
AND t.id = ci.movie_id
AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
AND n.id = ci.person_id
AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
AND ci.note IN ('@param0')
AND it1.info = '@param1'
AND it2.info = '@param2'
AND n.gender = '@param3'
AND n.name LIKE '@param4';
